===============================================================================================================================================================================================================

Rule-based AI
= alerts, thresholds, priorities, context rules

Expert-system AI
= racing knowledge encoded into tyre, damage, strategy, weather, consistency logic

Decision logic
= recommendations such as box, push, save fuel, recharge ERS, reset lap, adjust driving

Behavior intelligence
= radio timing, anti-spam, personality, memory, voice behavior

Race-engineer reasoning layer
= the combined high-level intelligence that explains what is happening and what the driver should do











